{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "13.0",
      "line_index": 13,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7584ce21",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "街の人がブルームの悪戯に困っている、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "13.2",
      "line_index": 13,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "7584ce21",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そのことを耳に確認のために街までやってきた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "17.0",
      "line_index": 17,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e6ff15c4",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あのメスガキ～～！！　もう滅茶苦茶だよ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "21.0",
      "line_index": 21,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "dd11c20c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ああもう……花壇メチャクチャ……何なんよアイツ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "24.0",
      "line_index": 24,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bddd6a6e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "（これはすごい……店の中はメチャクチャ、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "24.2",
      "line_index": 24,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "bddd6a6e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "花壇の花は全部引っこ抜かれてる……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "28.0",
      "line_index": 28,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "830253be",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "（しかし本当にブルームがやったのだろうか……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "28.2",
      "line_index": 28,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "830253be",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "もしかしたら別人の悪戯かも……確認しておいた方がいいな）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "32.0",
      "line_index": 32,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5345adcc",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "えっと……あの、少しお話いいですか……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "32.2",
      "line_index": 32,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "5345adcc",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "最近の悪戯の件ですけど、悪戯を直接目撃したりしました？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "35.0",
      "line_index": 35,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c60e0ad3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ああ、したよ！　生意気なツラのピンク髪のちっこい女だよ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "35.2",
      "line_index": 35,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "c60e0ad3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あいつ注意しても、ざまーみろとかほざいて笑いやがってさ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "38.0",
      "line_index": 38,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "92199242",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ピンク髪のちっこい女……間違いない、ブルームだな……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "43.0",
      "line_index": 43,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "204577f6",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "兄ちゃん、あのメスガキの知り合いか！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "46.0",
      "line_index": 46,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c644a8fd",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "まあ、一応は……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "51.0",
      "line_index": 51,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4592bf52",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "だったらバシっと躾けてくれよっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "51.2",
      "line_index": 51,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "4592bf52",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ああいうのは身体でわからせるしかないんだ！　頼むぜ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "54.0",
      "line_index": 54,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "72eb4d06",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "わ、わかりました。バシっとすることしますので",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "58.0",
      "line_index": 58,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "646fd443",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "（何度注意しても悪戯やめないな……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "58.2",
      "line_index": 58,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "646fd443",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "俺個人にだけ悪戯するなら大事にはするつもりはないが、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "58.4",
      "line_index": 58,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "646fd443",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "街の人に迷惑を掛けるのだけはさすがに見過ごせない……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "62.0",
      "line_index": 62,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ad134312",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "（もう心を鬼にして、キツーいお灸をすえてやらないと、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "62.2",
      "line_index": 62,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "ad134312",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あの性格は直りそうにないな……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "77.0",
      "line_index": 77,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "15922849",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "何しに来たのよっ、またブルームに馬鹿にされにきたの？　あはははっ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "80.0",
      "line_index": 80,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "11899aa7",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "お前、街の人に悪戯して困らせているようだな",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "86.0",
      "line_index": 86,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3e2c4ada",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "はぁ？　クソ人間のお前に何か関係あるわけ～？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "86.2",
      "line_index": 86,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "3e2c4ada",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ブルームがどこで何しようとお前には関係ないじゃんっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "89.0",
      "line_index": 89,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "dceca91c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "やれやれ……少しは反省の色を見せれば、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "89.2",
      "line_index": 89,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "dceca91c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "手心を加えてもいいかなって思っていたけど……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "95.0",
      "line_index": 95,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d9a197f9",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "フン、だ！　人間なんて悪魔に悪戯されるのがお似合いなんだっ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "95.2",
      "line_index": 95,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "d9a197f9",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "街の連中はこれからもブルームの玩具なんだからっ。きゃははははっ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "98.0",
      "line_index": 98,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ccd8ae63",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "仕方ない……これはすべてブルームが招いた事態だ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "98.2",
      "line_index": 98,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "ccd8ae63",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "しっかり反省させてやる……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "104.0",
      "line_index": 104,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "fc03dd8b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ちょ……！　お前、何いきなり服脱ぎだして……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "104.2",
      "line_index": 104,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "fc03dd8b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "きゃ……！　そ、そんなお粗末なおちんちん見せつけるなぁ～！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "107.0",
      "line_index": 107,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "63f53247",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "今日の俺は優しくないぞ！覚悟しろブルーム！　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "107.2",
      "line_index": 107,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "63f53247",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "しっかり身体で罪を償って反省しろっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "112.0",
      "line_index": 112,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "73e86f54",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "──きゃうっ！？　ちょっと！　離してよぉ！！　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "112.2",
      "line_index": 112,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "73e86f54",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "な、何する気なのっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "126.0",
      "line_index": 126,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d377b2e3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "──ひっ！？　お前！　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "126.2",
      "line_index": 126,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "d377b2e3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ま、まさかこのままブルームにえっちなことするつもりなのっ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "129.0",
      "line_index": 129,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c33acb82",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ああ、そのつもりだっ。いくら言葉で言ってもお前には無意味だからな。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "129.2",
      "line_index": 129,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "c33acb82",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "もう身体でわからせるしかない……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "132.0",
      "line_index": 132,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "719dca11",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "俺の言葉に本気なのを感じたのか、ブルームはジタバタともがく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "135.0",
      "line_index": 135,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b047c567",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "クソ人間の分際で、悪魔様にそんなことしていいと思っているわけっ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "138.0",
      "line_index": 138,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "884f588",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ああ、思ってるよ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "142.0",
      "line_index": 142,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9631bba6",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "クソ人間の分際でナマイキっ！！　どいてよっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "142.2",
      "line_index": 142,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "9631bba6",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "い、今謝れば許してあげるから……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "144.0",
      "line_index": 144,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "61d58eec",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ブルームは瞳に涙を浮かべ、逃げようと必死にもがく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "145.0",
      "line_index": 145,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1f9b2882",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その様子に心が痛むものの、心を鬼にしてブルームの身体を抑えつける。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "148.0",
      "line_index": 148,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d09af459",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "さあしっかり反省させてやるぞ……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "152.0",
      "line_index": 152,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1ed0116",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "──ひっ！？　や、やめ……マジで入れようとするなぁっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "152.2",
      "line_index": 152,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "1ed0116",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あっ！　先っぽ……ダメ、ダメ……ブルーム初めて──",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "160.0",
      "line_index": 160,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b4798348",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "はうううっ！？　う、あ……く、う、うううう……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "164.0",
      "line_index": 164,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f4a85803",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "挿入と同時にピストンを開始する。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "166.0",
      "line_index": 166,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "792bf275",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ブルームの中はまだあまり濡れていなかったが、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "166.2",
      "line_index": 166,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "792bf275",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それでも腰を動かし強引に膣中を抉っていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "169.0",
      "line_index": 169,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "21508e84",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "う、くぅ……く、苦しい……！　やめ、てぇ！　動かないでぇ……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "171.0",
      "line_index": 171,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "362d796",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "動くたびにあそこがじんわりと濡れ始め、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "171.2",
      "line_index": 171,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "362d796",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "徐々に引っ掛かりのようなものがなくなり、動きがスムーズになっていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "174.0",
      "line_index": 174,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f330d472",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "もう悪戯はしないか？　反省したか？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "178.0",
      "line_index": 178,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "cf4f5c47",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "だ、誰が……反省なんてぇ……あひぃっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "181.0",
      "line_index": 181,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "470fc027",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "まったくお前ってやつは……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "181.2",
      "line_index": 181,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "470fc027",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ここまですれば、少しはマシになるかと思ったんだけど……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "185.0",
      "line_index": 185,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "938de0ed",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "どうやら反省が足りないようだ……フンっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "189.0",
      "line_index": 189,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "878facff",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "んひぃっ！？♥　奥にぃぃぃ！♥　ダメ、ダメぇ！！♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "189.2",
      "line_index": 189,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "878facff",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ブルーム初めてなのにぃ……そ、そんなはげしくしないでぇっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "192.0",
      "line_index": 192,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "251bacd9",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "初めて？　そんなウソをついても無駄だぞっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "196.0",
      "line_index": 196,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "39d29968",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "う、ウソじゃないってぇ！　うあ、んぅぅぅっ！♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "196.2",
      "line_index": 196,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "39d29968",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "く、苦しい……息できないぃぃっ！　やめろって！　クソ人間っ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "198.0",
      "line_index": 198,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "fcd9e682",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "まだまだ抵抗できる気力があるのか、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "198.2",
      "line_index": 198,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "fcd9e682",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "この場から逃れようともがき続けるブルーム。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "200.0",
      "line_index": 200,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b826640a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それでもあそこを掻きまわされるたびにその抵抗も徐々に弱くなり、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "200.2",
      "line_index": 200,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "b826640a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "可愛い悲鳴が口から漏れ始めた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "203.0",
      "line_index": 203,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1341d043",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あひぃっ！♥　お、奥突かないでぇ……！♥　あ、あぁぁっ！♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "203.2",
      "line_index": 203,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "1341d043",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ダメ……これ、うう……お腹の奥、痺れて……あうっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "206.0",
      "line_index": 206,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2e4150b3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "（うう……勢いで始めたのはいいけど、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "206.2",
      "line_index": 206,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "2e4150b3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "これ……ブルームのあそこ、気持ち良過ぎ……！　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "206.4",
      "line_index": 206,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "2e4150b3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "長く持ちそうにないぞ……！！）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "209.0",
      "line_index": 209,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bf445351",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "無数の何かが肉棒に絡みつき、肉棒全体を舐めるように蠢く。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "210.0",
      "line_index": 210,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "56ffad84",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ゾクゾクした快感が何度も背筋を駆け上がり、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "210.2",
      "line_index": 210,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "56ffad84",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ピストンするたびに俺自身追い詰められていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "213.0",
      "line_index": 213,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e4838dd9",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "抜けぇ……抜いてぇ……はううっ！♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "213.2",
      "line_index": 213,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "e4838dd9",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そんな小刻みにぃ！♥　やめ……声出ちゃう……んあああぁっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "216.0",
      "line_index": 216,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "864c9574",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ならもう二度と悪戯はしないか？　人に迷惑を掛けないか？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "220.0",
      "line_index": 220,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "33dec472",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "フン、誰が……やめるものかぁ～！♥　んぅぅぅっ！！♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "220.2",
      "line_index": 220,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "33dec472",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "悪魔は人に迷惑を掛ける存在なんだよぉっ！♥　あぁぁんっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "223.0",
      "line_index": 223,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "485ec683",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "本当にお前ってやつは……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "223.2",
      "line_index": 223,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "485ec683",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ここまでされてどうしてそんなこと言えるんだ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "223.4",
      "line_index": 223,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "485ec683",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "こうなったら最後までしてやる……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "227.0",
      "line_index": 227,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7acca3d2",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "んひぃっ！♥　奥ばっかりやめてぇ……！♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "227.2",
      "line_index": 227,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "7acca3d2",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "こ、これ以上されたら……ああ、ダメ……やめ……！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "230.0",
      "line_index": 230,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "587ef7e5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "クソ人間のクソチンポにイかされちゃうっ！♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "230.2",
      "line_index": 230,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "587ef7e5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "悪魔なのに人間にイかされちゃうぅ！♥　んぅ！　ふああぁぁっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "232.0",
      "line_index": 232,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a44fc41d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "肉棒から精液を搾り取る様に、蠢く何かの動きが激しくなる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "233.0",
      "line_index": 233,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "486c203e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その動きに我慢の限界を迎えようとしていた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "236.0",
      "line_index": 236,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b5b53231",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ダメっ♥　ダメダメダメっ！♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "236.2",
      "line_index": 236,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "b5b53231",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ああ、もう……ふ、あ、あっ！♥　んああぁっ！！♥♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "247.0",
      "line_index": 247,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "80a2c2e5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "んんんんぅぅぅっ！♥　あう、うう……ふううううっ！♥♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "249.0",
      "line_index": 249,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5a71dd9",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "腰を乱暴に押し付けると、そのままブルームの中で果てる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "252.0",
      "line_index": 252,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "679afcfe",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "うう、これはお仕置きの中出しだ……！！　反省しろっ……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "256.0",
      "line_index": 256,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "dcff4cf3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "んお゛っ！♥　お……おお……膣内で射精してぇ……！♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "256.2",
      "line_index": 256,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "dcff4cf3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "クソ人間のクセにぃ……生意気ぃ……ううう……！！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "258.0",
      "line_index": 258,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "fc5ffdd8",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ビクンビクンと腰を跳ねらせ、何度も小さな絶頂を繰り返すブルーム。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "260.0",
      "line_index": 260,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1a55b602",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "中出しされた嫌悪感に表情を歪ませるが、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "260.2",
      "line_index": 260,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "1a55b602",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それでも絶頂の連続に、可愛い悲鳴を口から漏らし続ける。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "263.0",
      "line_index": 263,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9d30cd26",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "こんなか弱い悪魔に……お前絶対に許さないからな……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "263.2",
      "line_index": 263,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "9d30cd26",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "絶対に復讐してやる……！　街の連中にもお前にも悪戯しまくってやるぅ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "266.0",
      "line_index": 266,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ba2555e9",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "お前、ここまでされてまだそんなことが言えるのか……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "266.2",
      "line_index": 266,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "ba2555e9",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "まだ反省が足りないようだな……こうなりゃとことんやってやるっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "275.0",
      "line_index": 275,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1749a6e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "んおおっ！♥　んくっ！♥　や、やめ……あう゛っ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "277.0",
      "line_index": 277,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4b79f3ed",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "絶頂で過敏になっている膣を乱暴に掻き回すと、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "277.2",
      "line_index": 277,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "4b79f3ed",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ブルームは全身を震わせ快感が逃れようともがく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "279.0",
      "line_index": 279,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "569632db",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "執拗に膣奥を何度も突き、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "279.2",
      "line_index": 279,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "569632db",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "結合部から掻き出された精液にブルームの真っ白なお尻が白く汚れていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "282.0",
      "line_index": 282,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "28903bbc",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "やめ……はげしいのダメぇ！♥　も、もっと優しくぅ……あうっ！！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "285.0",
      "line_index": 285,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3e4f47a1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それなら反省するかっ？　もう二度と人間に悪さしないか！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "289.0",
      "line_index": 289,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c446d9a7",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "は、反省なんかしないぃぃぃ……！　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "289.2",
      "line_index": 289,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "c446d9a7",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "はおおおっ！！♥　奥ばっかりぃ……息詰まるぅぅっ……あぐっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "291.0",
      "line_index": 291,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6ec9992e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "快感の連続に、ブルームの瞳が虚ろになっていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "292.0",
      "line_index": 292,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b2803fe4",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それでも反省の色を見せず、感じながらも抵抗の意思を示し続ける。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "295.0",
      "line_index": 295,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f2f0ee1f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "（ここまで頑固だと思わなかった……。でも絶対に反省させないと……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "295.2",
      "line_index": 295,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "f2f0ee1f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そうしないといつか街を追い出される……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "299.0",
      "line_index": 299,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "571de5a7",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "（根は良いヤツなんだ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "299.2",
      "line_index": 299,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "571de5a7",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "みんなに好かれるヤツなんだ。気遣いできる可愛い子なんだ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "299.4",
      "line_index": 299,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "571de5a7",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "だから嫌われるような存在になってほしくないんだっ）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "303.0",
      "line_index": 303,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "616ad554",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "んああぁっ！♥　やめ、ろぉ！♥　おまんこおかしくなるぅ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "303.2",
      "line_index": 303,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "616ad554",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "　うう、ふあ、ああ……ダメ……また……すごいの……迫ってぇええっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "306.0",
      "line_index": 306,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3106d505",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "これ以上中に出されたくないだろう？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "306.2",
      "line_index": 306,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "3106d505",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "だからもう二度と悪戯しないと誓うんだっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "310.0",
      "line_index": 310,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e1e532cf",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "誰がそんなの……誓うかぁぁっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "313.0",
      "line_index": 313,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5cc5726e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それならもう一度中出ししてやるっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "317.0",
      "line_index": 317,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5eb1d7be",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "やめ……やめろぉぉおっ！♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "317.2",
      "line_index": 317,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "5eb1d7be",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ふ、ふあっ！♥　あっ♥　あああーーーっ！！♥♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "328.0",
      "line_index": 328,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5c43521c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "んひぃぃぃっ！♥　また中にぃ……う、ううううっ！！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "331.0",
      "line_index": 331,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f763870d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "うう……！　どうだ、これで懲りただろうっ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "335.0",
      "line_index": 335,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b0c39778",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "んひぃ……ひぃっ！♥　だ、誰が……懲りたりするかぁ……んおおっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "337.0",
      "line_index": 337,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bdab7f56",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "強烈な絶頂に息も絶え絶えなブルーム。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "338.0",
      "line_index": 338,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "57e6ad3b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それでも反抗的な態度を改めず、悪態をつき続ける。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "341.0",
      "line_index": 341,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ce5bd239",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "何でわかってくれないんだ……みんなに嫌われてもいいのか？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "345.0",
      "line_index": 345,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "191293f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "フン……んぅ！♥　ブルームは悪魔なんだ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "345.2",
      "line_index": 345,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "191293f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "人間に好かれる必要なんてないんだぁ……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "348.0",
      "line_index": 348,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "192935e0",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "悪戯は絶対にやめない……一生続けてやるぅぅぅ……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "351.0",
      "line_index": 351,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a1ad5de0",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "はぁ～……これは思いのほか時間がかかりそうだ……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "351.2",
      "line_index": 351,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "a1ad5de0",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "でも俺が絶対にお前を変えてやる……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "351.4",
      "line_index": 351,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "a1ad5de0",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "みんなから好かれる悪魔にしてやるからっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "355.0",
      "line_index": 355,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4ab974c6",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ひいいっ！？♥　もうやめ……ああ、ふあああぁぁぁっ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "357.0",
      "line_index": 357,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2ed76e99",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "再び肉棒でブルームのあそこを掻き回す。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "359.0",
      "line_index": 359,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d072e5f7",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "今度こそ反省するように祈りながら、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "359.2",
      "line_index": 359,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "d072e5f7",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "こみ上げてきたものを再びブルームの中に注ぎ込むのであった。",
      "zh": ""
    }
  ]
}
